Package de.mrms.api

Interface Summary
DataRepository Implementations represent a repository of information about the music catalog, users and their preferences.
Recommendation Implementations of this interface represent a song recommendations including score, explanation and song information.
RecommendationFactory Implementations of this interface create recommendation objects.
Recommender Implementations of this interface can recommend items for users.
Song Implementations of this interface represent a song and its information.
User Implementations of this interface represent a user and its information.
 

Class Summary
AbstractRecommender Skeletal implementation of Recommender.
